Privacy Policy for Wreck My Car Prank

Last updated: January 25, 2026

This Privacy Policy describes Our policies and procedures on the collection, use, and disclosure of Your information when You use the Service, including features that allow AI-generated content, and explains Your privacy rights and how the law protects You.

By using the Service, You agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

Interpretation and Definitions

Collecting and Using Your Personal Data
Types of Data Collected
Personal Data

We do not require You to provide personally identifiable information to use the core features of the Service.
However, certain features may involve the processing of images or usage data as described below.

Images and AI-Generated Content

When You use features that allow uploading images or generating images using artificial intelligence:

Images are processed only for the purpose of providing the requested functionality (e.g. generating prank images).

Uploaded images may include vehicles or surroundings but are not intended to identify individuals.

We do not use uploaded images or generated images to identify You or any other person.

Images are not used to train AI models owned or controlled by Us.

Usage Data

Usage Data is collected automatically and may include:

IP address

Device type and operating system

App interactions and feature usage

Diagnostic and performance data

Use of Artificial Intelligence (AI)

The Service includes features that use third-party artificial intelligence technologies to generate images.

How AI Is Used

AI is used solely to generate visual content requested by the user.

Image processing may be performed by trusted third-party AI service providers.

These providers process data only on Our behalf and under contractual obligations to protect user privacy.

Data Handling

Uploaded images may be temporarily transmitted to AI service providers for processing.

Images are not stored longer than necessary to provide the Service.

We do not associate AI-generated images with user identities.

No Training or Profiling

User content is not used for behavioral profiling.

User images and prompts are not used to train or improve AI models.

Use of Your Personal Data

The Company may use Personal Data to:

Provide and maintain the Service

Monitor usage and improve functionality

Respond to user requests and support inquiries

Communicate updates related to the Service

Comply with legal obligations

Sharing of Your Personal Data

We may share Your information only in the following situations:

With Service Providers (including AI providers) strictly for operating the Service

For legal compliance or business transfers

With Your explicit consent

We do not sell Your personal data.

Retention of Your Personal Data

Images uploaded for AI features are retained only as long as necessary to generate the requested result.

Usage Data is retained for internal analysis and security purposes.

Data may be retained longer if required by law.

Transfer of Your Personal Data

Your data may be processed outside Your country. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect Your data.

Delete Your Personal Data

You may request deletion of Your data by contacting Us.
Temporary image data used for AI generation is automatically deleted within a short period.

